{"tid":255872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首4個月強姦案急增77%","createTime":"2017-05-24T06:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T06:14:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0724e4b877665935e284af75d75ee57c72ef113d","tid":255872,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20031728&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20031728%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170524&d=IZWl12S5z6lUnueYSkvqYU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c2b78e51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20031728%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170524&h=bfa4033d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20031728&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170524</a><br />\n<br />\n首4個月強姦案急增77%<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n李家超（左）指電騙案數目持續上升，提醒市民小心。 伍嘉亮攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港今年首4個月總罪案錄得18,825宗，較去年同期跌2.5%；因犯罪而被捕總人數達10,066人。惟強姦和非禮較去年同期升76.9%及11.1%。署理保安局局長李家超稱，本港罪案情況平穩，數字有下跌趨勢，但電騙案持續增多，提醒市民小心。<br />\n<br />\n近兩月電騙大增<br />\n<br />\n李家超昨出席撲滅罪行委員會會議後指，今年首4個月總體罪案有18,825宗，暴力罪案則有2,888宗，較去年同期跌7.4%。其中，強姦有23宗和非禮有311宗，較去年同期分別升76.9%及11.1%。毒品罪行方面，今年首4個月有802人因涉及毒品被捕，較去年同期下跌3%，但撿獲毒品以忘我類及大麻最多，分別是去年同期的6倍和3倍。至於盜竊案中，失車案較去年同期升25.9%，由去年139架增至今年175架。<br />\n他又指，現有150個國家受勒索軟件WannaCry影響，涉及逾30萬受害人。截止昨日為止，警方接到3宗報案，但事主均無付贖金，故無任何損失；電腦保安事故協調中心則接到34宗相關個案，當中31宗涉及家用電腦，政府會繼續與各單位保持聯繫，向公眾交代新發展及影響。<br />\n至於電騙案數目雖與去年相若，1月及2月分別錄得20至30宗，但3月和4月數字升至約100宗，李提醒市民要加強警惕。<br />\n■記者張文鈴<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=IZWl12S5z6lUnueYSkvqYU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=768bbe57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"cf531dfd2a2d9c7c2f1249e3bb5707343803dd42","tid":255872,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170524/large/a0805a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170524%2Flarge%2Fa0805a.gif&h=c13ae4fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1752eb7d68b8679e3c85462f7034867bd639c6f5","tid":255872,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:13:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9612b837ac646894a7e24cb24c2fcde9837c8555","tid":255872,"uid":107156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}